AUDIO: 'crashes out of all things and a lot more. So, let\'s jump right in. First up, this AI is pretty cool. It\'s called Shape LLM Omni, and this is a multimodal model for 3D generation. Think of it as'

[01:03] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'like a chatbot that can understand and create 3D objects. So, this can take in a text prompt or an image and generate a 3D model. You can also get it to edit 3D models further just by prompting it like'

