[03:13] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'called Flow Mo. Think of this as like a plug-in which you can add on top of a video generator to improve the results. It can make the video look smoother and more coherent. So, here are some'

[03:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'examples. Let\'s say you\'re using one 2.1, the 1.3 billion parameter version, and you want to get a boy to fly a kite in a field like this. Well, on the left is the raw generation, and you can see'

[03:37] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'the kite is kind of messed up. There\'s an extra kite that appears out of nowhere. But after plugging this through Flow Mo, it kind of makes the quality a bit better and more realistic. At least you don\'t get this extra kite that'

[03:50] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'appears from nowhere. Or here\'s another example. As you can see on the left, just the raw output is pretty awful with her limbs warping around everywhere. But after plugging this into Flowmo, it makes the motion a lot more coherent.'

[04:02] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Here\'s another example where the prompt is a dolphin jumping out of ocean waves. And as you can see, after adding Flow Mo, the generation is just a lot better. Here, the prompt is a child jumping on a'

[04:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'trampoline. And as you can see, Flo\'s generation is just a lot more realistic. Here\'s another example where the prompt is a helicopter flying over a forest. Really quickly, here\'s how it works. So,'

[04:26] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'at a very high level, it analyzes the video as it\'s being generated and adjusts the motions to make it smoother and more natural. It does this by measuring the patch-wise variance of the video, which is like measuring how much'

[04:40] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'the motion changes from one frame to the next. And by reducing this variance, Flow Mo can create more realistic and coherent motion. The nice thing is this plugin is model agnostic. So here they\'ve shown that you can use this on'

[04:53] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'top of one by Alibaba, which is the best open- source video generator out there right now, but you can also apply this to another open- source model called Cog Videoo X. Anyways, they\'ve released the code already. So, if you click on this'

[05:05] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
