[05:31] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'the description below. Next up, this AI is pretty cool. It\'s called Native Resolution Image Synthesis, and they\'ve created an AI called a native resolution diffusion transformer, or NIT for short.'

[05:43] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'And this can create images in any size and aspect ratio without needing to be trained on these specific sizes. Now, if you\'ve been playing around with image generation, you\'ll probably find that'

