VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'most image generators do well only with certain image sizes. So, for example, SDXL or Flux generates the best images if they are 1024x1024. And then other image generators like Google\'s Imagine can'

[06:08] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'only generate certain aspect ratios. You can\'t really specify custom dimensions. But this AI, NIT, can generate the same quality of image regardless of aspect ratio or the size of the image. So, here'

